  <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.inghams.co.ukk/lakes-mountains-holidays/resorts/slovenia/portoroz">Portoroz</a> is a more cosmopolitan 'Riviera' style resort, boasting a floral promenade as its main feature, rightfully giving the town its name - 'Port of Roses'. A distinct flavour of the Italian Riviera pervades here with elegant Portoroz hotels, restaurants, cafés and boutiques, stretching for about 4km along the shoreline. If you care to venture inland you can combine your holiday in Portoroz with other Slovenian resorts such as <a href="/{localLink:73208af5-f6cc-47fb-8531-8803c9f7af18}" title="Ljubljana">Ljubljana</a>, <a href="/{localLink:cd13917a-a056-4f56-bd6c-a4bc9ee85985}" title="Lake Bled">Bled</a> and <a href="/{localLink:ac7617b0-3f78-4856-9127-b729b7d88fd5}" title="Lake Bohinj">Bohinj</a>.</p>
<p> </p>
